["Lorna Forde (born 24 June 1952) is a Barbadian sprinter. She competed in the women's 100 metres and women's 400 metres at the 1976 Summer Olympics. Forde competed in the 4 \u00d7 400 metres relay at the 1972 Summer Olympics. Forde won bronze in the 400 metres and finished seventh in the 200 metres at the 1975 Pan American Games.[1]","This biographical article relating to Barbadian athletics is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it."]